...but no matter how hard Kreacher tried.
he could not do it.

496
00:45:23.565 --> 00:45:25.157
Well. where is it now?

497
00:45:25.801 --> 00:45:30.397
- Did someone take it?
- He came in the night.

498
00:45:30.572 --> 00:45:35.236
He took many things.
including the locket.

499
00:45:35.410 --> 00:45:36.934
Who did?

500
00:45:37.613 --> 00:45:39.205
Who was it. Kreacher?

501
00:45:41.750 --> 00:45:44.412
Mundungus.

502
00:45:44.586 --> 00:45:48.078
Mundungus Fletcher.

503
00:45:49.157 --> 00:45:50.749
Find him.

504
00:46:09.745 --> 00:46:11.406
[DOOR OPENS]

505
