Hey. losers.

507
00:46:21.657 --> 00:46:23.921
He isn't here.

508
00:46:37.539 --> 00:46:39.939
As your new Minister for Magic...

509
00:46:40.142 --> 00:46:45.307
...I promise to restore
this temple of tolerance...

510
00:46:45.480 --> 00:46:47.141
...to its former glory.

511
00:46:48.550 --> 00:46:50.381
Therefore. beginning today...

512
