...if you have nothing to hide.

516
00:47:05.600 --> 00:47:07.192
[CHUCKLES]

517
00:47:09.571 --> 00:47:11.163
- How much?
- Two Galleons.

518
00:47:11.340 --> 00:47:13.831
Come on. time is money. Cheers. pal.

519
00:47:14.009 --> 00:47:15.943
MAN 1: Snatchers!
MAN 2: Move out of the way.

520
00:47:22.150 --> 00:47:23.617
- I told you.
MAN 3: Get out.

521
00:47:23.785 --> 00:47:24.809
MAN 2:
Squash him.

522
00:47:29.658 --> 00:47:31.125
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

523
00:47:31.526 --> 00:47:33.858
[RON PLAYING BEETHOVEN'S
"F�R ELISE" OFF-KEY]

524
00:47:34.029 --> 00:47:35.656
Be a bit gentler.

525
00:47:39.501 --> 00:47:41.492
[HERMIONE PLAYING
BEETHOVEN'S "F�R ELISE"]

526
00:47:47.042 --> 00:47:49.374
[RON CONTINUES
PLAYING OFF-KEY]

527
00:47:57.185 --> 00:47:59.847
[WHIRRING]

528
00:48:01.757 --> 00:48:03.884
They have flesh memories.

529
