When Scrimgeour first gave it to you.
I thought it might open at your touch.

530
00:48:12.401 --> 00:48:15.165
That Dumbledore had hidden
something inside it.

531
00:48:15.404 --> 00:48:17.065
<i>MAN [ON RADIO]:
Many of you are wondering...

532
00:48:17.239 --> 00:48:20.174
<i>...why Voldemort has yet to show himself
now that he has vanquished...

533
00:48:20.342 --> 00:48:23.402
<i>...the most powerful symbol of opposition
to him and his followers.

534
00:48:25.447 --> 00:48:26.471
MUNDUNGUS [MUFFLED]:
Get off.

535
00:48:26.648 --> 00:48:29.412
Harry Potter. so long it's been.

536
00:48:29.885 --> 00:48:31.216
MUNDUNGUS [IN NORMAL VOICE]:
Get off me.

537
00:48:31.653 --> 00:48:33.985
[ALL GRUNTING]

538
00:48:36.825 --> 00:48:40.761
As requested.
Kreacher has returned with the thief...

539
00:48:40.929 --> 00:48:42.920
<i>- Expellliarmus.
- ... Mundungus Fletcher.

540
00:48:43.098 --> 00:48:46.295
What you playing at? Setting a pair
of bleeding house-elves after me.

541
00:48:46.468 --> 00:48:47.958
Dobby was only trying to help.

542
00:48:48.136 --> 00:48:52.505
Dobby saw Kreacher in Diagon Alley.
which Dobby thought was curious.

543
00:48:52.674 --> 00:48:57.008
And then Dobby heard Kreacher
mention Harry Potter's name.

544
00:48:57.179 --> 00:49:00.012
- I just-
- And then Dobby saw Kreacher...

545
00:49:00.182 --> 00:49:02.980
- ... talking with the thief. Mundungus-
- I'm no thief.

546
00:49:03.151 --> 00:49:06.086
You foul little- Git.

547
00:49:06.488 --> 00:49:10.891
I'm a purveyor
of rare and wondrous objects.

548
00:49:11.059 --> 00:49:12.924
You're a thief. Dung. Everyone knows it.

549
00:49:13.094 --> 00:49:16.063
Master Weasley.
so good to see you again.

550
00:49:16.231 --> 00:49:17.255
Wicked trainers.

551
00:49:17.432 --> 00:49:18.831
