Listen. I panicked that night. all right?

553
00:49:23.405 --> 00:49:25.635
Could I help it
if Mad-Eye fell off his broom?

554
00:49:27.642 --> 00:49:29.075
KREACHER: You...
HERMIONE: Tell the truth.

555
00:49:29.244 --> 00:49:32.008
When you turned this place over-
Don't deny it.

556
00:49:32.180 --> 00:49:33.704
- you found a locket. am I right?

557
00:49:33.882 --> 00:49:36.146
