No. he's worried
he didn't get enough money for it.

560
00:49:40.222 --> 00:49:41.746
Bleeding give it away. didn't I?

561
00:49:41.923 --> 00:49:42.947
[SIGHS]

562
00:49:43.124 --> 00:49:46.252
There I was.
flogging me wares in Diagon Alley...

563
