570
00:50:49.391 --> 00:50:51.382
[SNORING]

571
00:50:54.195 --> 00:50:57.961
Right. remember what we said.

572
00:50:58.233 --> 00:51:01.964
Don't speak to anyone
unless absolutely necessary.

573
00:51:02.237 --> 00:51:07.140
Just try and act normal.
Do what everybody else is doing.

574
00:51:07.576 --> 00:51:10.704
If we do that. then with a bit of luck.
we'll get inside.

575
00:51:10.879 --> 00:51:12.471
- And then-
- It gets really tricky.

576
00:51:12.647 --> 00:51:14.512
- Correct.
- Yeah.

577
00:51:14.683 --> 00:51:17.584
- This is completely mental.
- Completely.

578
00:51:17.752 --> 00:51:19.777
The world�s mental.

579
00:51:19.955 --> 00:51:21.388
Come on...

580
00:51:21.990 --> 00:51:24.424
...we've got a Horcrux to find.

581
00:51:50.285 --> 00:51:52.276
