Gotta tell you.
I'm starting to freak out a bit.

592
00:53:26.314 --> 00:53:30.808
How long did you say this batch
of Polyjuice would last. Hermione?

593
00:53:31.352 --> 00:53:32.376
I didn't.

594
00:53:32.554 --> 00:53:33.578
[ELEVATOR DINGS]

595
00:53:39.561 --> 00:53:41.495
