It's still raining inside my office.
That's two days now.

597
00:53:48.069 --> 00:53:49.832
Have you tried an umbrella?

598
00:53:50.805 --> 00:53:53.740
You do realize I'm going downstairs.
don't you. Cattermole?

599
00:53:54.309 --> 00:53:58.268
- Downstairs?
- To interrogate your wife.

600
00:53:59.180 --> 00:54:03.116
Now. if my wife's blood status
were in doubt...

601
00:54:03.284 --> 00:54:06.185
