I think I might just make that a priority.

603
00:54:12.494 --> 00:54:14.689
You have one hour.

604
00:54:26.441 --> 00:54:32.107
Oh. my God. What am I gonna do?
My wife's all alone downstairs.

605
00:54:32.413 --> 00:54:36.679
- Ron. you don't have a wife.
- Oh. right.

606
00:54:36.851 --> 00:54:38.819
<i>FEMALE VOICE [OVER SPEAKERS]:
Level 2.

607
00:54:39.621 --> 00:54:41.748
RON:
But how do I stop it raining?

608
00:54:41.923 --> 00:54:44.517
<i>HERMIONE:
Try "Finite Incantatem. "

609
00:54:44.692 --> 00:54:46.557
<i>FEMALE VOICE:
Department of Magical Law Enforcement...

610
00:54:46.728 --> 00:54:48.161
<i>...and Improper Use of Magic Department.

611
00:54:48.329 --> 00:54:50.297
HERMIONE:
This is you. Ron.

612
00:54:54.536 --> 00:54:59.371
<i>Finite Incantatem. Okay.
And if that doesn't work...?

613
00:55:11.286 --> 00:55:14.221
<i>FEMALE VOICE: Level 1.
Minister of Magic and support staff.

614
00:55:14.389 --> 00:55:16.516
If we don't locate Umbridge
within the hour...

615
00:55:16.691 --> 00:55:18.682
...we go find Ron
and come back another day.

616
00:55:18.860 --> 00:55:19.884
- Deal?
- Yes.

617
00:55:23.464 --> 00:55:25.796
Ah. Mafalda. Travers sent you. did he?

618
00:55:25.967 --> 00:55:29.027
Good. we�ll go straight down.

619
00:55:31.372 --> 00:55:33.897
Albert. aren't you getting out?

620
00:55:41.816 --> 00:55:42.976
