[HONKS]

624
00:57:01.796 --> 00:57:03.195
<i>[WHISPERS]
Accio locket.

625
00:57:57.885 --> 00:58:01.048
MAN: All right. all right.
Let's calm down. shall we?

626
00:58:01.956 --> 00:58:04.424
Let's get back to work. please.

627
00:58:05.226 --> 00:58:07.057
Calm down.

628
00:58:12.400 --> 00:58:14.095
Runcorn.

629
00:58:21.909 --> 00:58:23.672
Morning.

630
00:58:25.380 --> 00:58:27.814
Ron. it's me.

631
00:58:27.982 --> 00:58:31.816
Harry.
Blimey. forgot what you looked like.

632
00:58:31.986 --> 00:58:33.419
Where's Hermione?

633
00:58:33.588 --> 00:58:37.024
She's gone down to the courtrooms.
with Umbridge.

634
00:58:37.191 --> 00:58:38.215
[ELEVATOR DOOR OPENS]

635
