RON:
Bloody cold down here.

636
00:58:46.167 --> 00:58:49.762
ALDERTON:
I'm a half-blood. My father was a wizard.

637
00:58:49.937 --> 00:58:52.269
William Alderton.
He worked here for 30 years.

638
00:58:52.440 --> 00:58:55.876
Perhaps you know him.
Always wore his jacket inside out.

639
00:58:56.044 --> 00:58:58.512
No. there's been a mistake.
I'm half-blood. you see.

640
00:58:58.679 --> 00:59:01.876
We must go back. I'm half-blood.

641
00:59:11.993 --> 00:59:14.086
UMBRIDGE: Mary Elizabeth Cattermole?
MARY: Yes.

642
00:59:14.262 --> 00:59:19.199
UMBRIDGE: Of 27 Chislehurst Gardens.
Great Tollling. Evesham?

643
00:59:19.367 --> 00:59:20.391
MARY: Yes.
- It's here.

644
00:59:20.568 --> 00:59:25.369
Mother to Maisie. Elllie and Alfred?
Wife to Reginald?

645
00:59:29.577 --> 00:59:30.635
Reg?

646
