652
01:00:06.714 --> 01:00:09.148
MARY:
I didn't take it.

653
01:00:10.384 --> 01:00:16.186
I got it in Diagon Alley. at Ollivander's.
when I was 11.

654
01:00:17.625 --> 01:00:20.116
It chose me.

655
01:00:21.496 --> 01:00:23.259
You're lying.

656
01:00:23.698 --> 01:00:28.260
Wands only choose witches.
and you are not a witch.

657
