But I am.

658
01:00:30.905 --> 01:00:33.965
Tell them. Reg. Tell them what I am.

659
01:00:36.511 --> 01:00:37.876
Reg. tell them what I am.

660
01:00:41.249 --> 01:00:43.240
[WHIRRING AND CHITTERING]

661
01:00:47.855 --> 01:00:49.618
What on earth are you doing. Albert?

662
01:00:52.527 --> 01:00:54.427
You're lying. Dolores.

663
01:00:56.797 --> 01:00:59.357
And one mustn't tell lies.

664
01:01:00.168 --> 01:01:01.465
<i>Stupefy!

665
01:01:02.937 --> 01:01:04.768
[GRUNTS]

666
