MARY:
Oh. Oh. Oh.

672
01:01:56.824 --> 01:01:58.849
Mary. go home.

673
01:02:00.294 --> 01:02:01.761
Get the kids.

674
01:02:01.929 --> 01:02:05.296
I'll meet you there. We have to get out
