675
01:02:05.466 --> 01:02:07.934
Mary. do as I say.

676
01:02:22.350 --> 01:02:23.510
Mary?

677
01:02:25.152 --> 01:02:27.052
Who's that?

678
01:02:28.189 --> 01:02:31.181
Long story. Nice meeting you.

679
01:02:31.359 --> 01:02:32.724
MAN 1:
It's Harry Potter.

680
01:02:33.427 --> 01:02:35.395
It's Harry. Harry Potter.

681
01:02:35.563 --> 01:02:37.588
MAN 2: There he is.
- Get him!

682
01:02:37.765 --> 01:02:39.858
MAN 3: Get him!
MAN 4: Stop him!

683
01:02:46.073 --> 01:02:47.097
[MAN 5 GRUNTS]

684
01:02:51.779 --> 01:02:52.939
MAN 6: Watch out.
MAN 7: Look out.

685
01:02:53.314 --> 01:02:54.713
MAN 8:
This way!

686
01:02:55.449 --> 01:02:57.246
[HARRY GRUNTING]

687
01:03:07.194 --> 01:03:08.957
[YELLS]

688
