694
01:04:10.257 --> 01:04:13.522
Harry. Harry. quickly. in my bag.

695
01:04:13.694 --> 01:04:16.219
There's a bottle labeled
"Essence of Dittany. "

696
01:04:18.799 --> 01:04:21.597
Shh. Shh.

697
01:04:21.769 --> 01:04:24.465
Okay. okay. Quickly.

698
01:04:25.239 --> 01:04:27.332
<i>- Accio Dittany.
HERMIONE: Shh.

699
01:04:27.708 --> 01:04:30.438
