700
01:04:30.611 --> 01:04:32.101
Hermione. his arm.

701
01:04:32.279 --> 01:04:34.270
I know. just do it.

702
01:04:35.015 --> 01:04:36.744
It's okay.

703
01:04:38.018 --> 01:04:41.977
- Okay. it's gonna sting a little bit.
- What happened? I thought we meant...

704
01:04:42.156 --> 01:04:44.886
