HERMIONE: We were. We were. Shh.

705
01:04:45.059 --> 01:04:46.890
It's all right. One more. one more.

706
01:04:47.061 --> 01:04:51.589
We were there. we were there.
but Yaxley had hold of me. and I...

707
01:04:51.766 --> 01:04:54.792
I knew once he'd seen where we were.
we couldn�t stay...

708
01:04:54.969 --> 01:04:58.097
...so I brought us here...

709
01:04:58.572 --> 01:05:01.200
