716
01:05:38.412 --> 01:05:40.107
You can get going on the tent.

717
01:05:40.781 --> 01:05:42.612
<i>- Tent?
HERMIONE: Protego Totalum.

718
01:05:42.783 --> 01:05:44.910
HARRY:
Where am I supposed to find a tent?

719
01:05:45.085 --> 01:05:49.385
<i>HERMIONE:
Repello Muggletum. Muffliato.

720
01:05:59.700 --> 01:06:01.600
HERMIONE:
You first.

721
01:06:04.605 --> 01:06:06.698
<i>HARRY:
Dissendium.

722
01:06:11.178 --> 01:06:13.408
[LOCKET CHITTERING]

723
01:06:20.321 --> 01:06:22.221
<i>Incendio.

724
01:06:24.959 --> 01:06:27.154
