725
01:06:27.628 --> 01:06:29.653
<i>Expulso.

726
01:06:36.871 --> 01:06:38.998
<i>Diffindo.

727
01:06:40.441 --> 01:06:41.465
<i>Reducto.

728
01:06:48.883 --> 01:06:50.874
[PANTING]

729
01:06:51.952 --> 01:06:53.943
[CHITTERING CONTINUES]

